ccording to a new\nclassification.In a clear way the basic mechanical steps of all throws, and\nalso show hidden connections, similarities and differences among judo throwing\ntechniques, making this reassessment particularly useful from a didactic point\nof view. Demonstrate that this biomechanical approach is also able to\nunderstand how new and innovative technical variations are born.Our\nreassessment helps clarifying his concept and facilitates teachers and coaches\nin their professional work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jun 2012 07:14:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Jun 2012 11:04:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-08"}
